entry.title: Diabetes Prediction Model
entry.content:
Diabetes Predictor

Using Tensorflow and national CDC data, we created a model to predict diabetes with 92.5% accuracy

entry.title: Our Official Founding
entry.content: The Montana Rural Health Data Science Center was finally officially created today! Now we are beginning to deploy our math models throughout the state, starting with a predictor for diabetes.
